caption: Great place for food and games. I love the street cart fries loaded with pink aglioli sauce, chopped veggies, feta cheese and kalamata olives. The Mediterranean wrap with beef and lamb gyros is tasty too. They serve a variety of   beers and sangria. The atmosphere is artsy, eclectic and hip and the patio seating outside is pleasant.

Visiting CA for our anniversary!  Pros: amazing food, vegan friendly, awesome and fast service!  Cons: this is in a rough part of town so I wouldn't suggest going at dark, it is not a place you sit down at.  Deliciousness! They need more of these!
